Reimagined the brand’s “break” proposition by encouraging meaningful offline moments in an increasingly digital world.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">Moment Marketing</span><span class="chip">Lifestyle Ad</span></div></div></article><article class="project-card"><div class="project-image"><img src="assets/mamaearth_clean_beauty.png" alt="Mamaearth campaign"></div><div class="project-content"><h3>Mamaearth Clean Beauty Ad</h3><p>Positioned the product through a clean visual identity that highlighted sustainability, simplicity, and natural ingredients.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">Minimal Design</span><span class="chip">Beauty Branding</span></div></div></article>
